<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-16300] Cassandra 2.2 doesn&apos;t satisfy Java 1.7 language level</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16300</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think that 2.2 needs to satisfy Java 1.7 language level. However, there are a few places where newer syntax is used:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/net/MessagingService.java#L779&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;MessagingService&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/utils/ExecutorUtils.java#L36-L47&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;ExecutorUtils&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/utils/Throwables.java#L36&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Throwables&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.2/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/config/YamlConfigurationLoader.java#L142&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;YamlConfigurationLoader&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/cassandra-2.2/test/unit/org/apache/cassandra/config/YamlConfigurationLoaderTest.java#L38&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;YamlConfigurationLoaderTest&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;If I&apos;m right and we really need 1.7 language level we should fix those, which seems quite straightforward.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
