                            <comment id="17238717" author="adelapena" created="Wed, 25 Nov 2020 12:21:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/adelapena/cassandra/142/workflows/8c40cd44-a18a-413f-8d9b-9f47a208acb9&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;CircleCI results&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17243401" author="edimitrova" created="Thu, 3 Dec 2020 17:47:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I know we don&apos;t have Java 7 CI infrastructure, but were unit tests run at least locally? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17243940" author="adelapena" created="Fri, 4 Dec 2020 11:07:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=e.dimitrova&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;e.dimitrova&quot;&gt;e.dimitrova&lt;/a&gt; Yes, I&apos;m attaching a unit test run with source.version=1.7 and&#160;source.test.version=1.8.&#160;Locally in only find failures in &lt;tt&gt;SSTableRewriterTest&lt;/tt&gt;, but I get the same failures with&#160;source.version=1.8 and without the patch, so I&apos;m assuming it&apos;s caused by my environment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17244059" author="edimitrova" created="Fri, 4 Dec 2020 15:33:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adelapena&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adelapena&quot;&gt;adelapena&lt;/a&gt;! LGTM +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17247939" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 11 Dec 2020 14:05:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;LGTM +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17247969" author="adelapena" created="Fri, 11 Dec 2020 15:32:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the reviews. Committed to cassandra-2.2 as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/20d1f9a69c18bfd11607063ec16fd24d1c835b55&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;20d1f9a69c18bfd11607063ec16fd24d1c835b55&lt;/a&gt; and merged up&#160; discarding the changes in more recent branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
